"title": "6646: eternal life, gift of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6646: eternal life, gift of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Eternal life cannot be earned or merited but must be received as a gift from God.</p>\n<h2>Fruitless attempts to earn eternal life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:39-John5:40\">JHN 5:39–5:40</a></strong> <em>It is possible to study the mere letter of Scripture while ignoring coming to its focus, Jesus Christ</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:11-Gal3:12\">GAL 3:11–3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:20\">ROM 3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:28\">ROM 3:28</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is the source of eternal life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:11-1John5:12\">1JN 5:11–5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:25-John11:26\">JHN 11:25–11:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6\">JHN 14:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:21\">ROM 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:9\">HEB 5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:12\">HEB 9:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:1\">2TI 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:10\">2TI 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:20\">1JN 5:20</a></p>\n<h2>Eternal life is a gift</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:27\">JHN 6:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:28\">JHN 10:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:7\">ROM 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:15-Rom5:17\">ROM 5:15–5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:8-Eph2:9\">EPH 2:8–2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:7\">1PE 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:3\">2PE 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>Received by faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:36\">JHN 3:36</a></strong> <em>Faith in Jesus Christ, God's son, is the only way to gain eternal life.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24\">JHN 5:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:40\">JHN 6:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:31\">JHN 20:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:16\">1TI 1:16</a></p>\n<h3>The need for personal commitment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:25-John12:26\">JHN 12:25–12:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:14\">MAT 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:37-Mark8:38\">MRK 8:37–8:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:18\">ACT 11:18</a> <em>Repentance is the first step of commitment</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:8-Rom6:11\">ROM 6:8–6:11</a></p>",
